{"tid":1939690,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"因應疫情 奧地利宣佈5人以上集會為非法集結 同時禁蒙面法未取消 無醫學證明不準公眾場所用口罩","createTime":"2020-03-23T09:31:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-23T10:10:59.000Z","uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2a099587fb3f0787aa0b3fa1bea7927c6e748c7e","tid":1939690,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T09:31:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20200315003521-260408?chdtv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20200315003521-260408%3Fchdtv&d=Eps995EZp4R4ibMzYmnfryLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=1077272b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20200315003521-260408?chdtv</a><br />\n奧地利15日公布一系列嚴格的公共場所活動限制措施，敦促所有民眾自主隔離、禁止5人以上聚集，並加強入境管制。奧地利總理辦公室聲明稱，「我們要求奧地利公民進行自主隔離，意即人們只能和共同生活的人進行日常交往。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新措施將於16日起實施，政府要求人們只有在從事無法推遲的工作、採購必要的食品，以及幫助他人時才能出門。而5人以上的集會僅限於以對抗疫情為目的。奧地利總理庫爾茨表示，室外場所從15日起部署警力，遇到人群聚集將予以遣散。<br />\n<br />\n奧地利衛生當局統計，至15日上午，該國新冠肺炎確診病例累計達800例，死亡病例1例。繼13日開始對蒂羅爾州疫情嚴重的兩個市鎮實施封閉隔離後，奧地利從14日起對克恩滕州海利根布盧特鎮進行為期14天的封閉隔離。<br />\n<br />\n奧地利首都維也納正在加緊建設第一個方艙醫院。該醫院由維也納會展中心臨時改建而成，將於下周提供880張床位，用來收治新冠肺炎輕症患者。奧地利政府14日也推出總額40億歐元的一系列危機救助計畫，以因應新冠肺炎疫情對經濟造成的影響。<br />\n<br />\n(中時 )<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1721283/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E6%88%B4%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E9%87%8D%E7%BD%B0%E9%80%BE%E5%8D%83%E5%85%83-%E5%A5%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%A9%E8%A6%8F%E5%AE%9A%E6%9C%89%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E7%B4%99%E6%89%8D%E8%83%BD%E6%88%B4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1721283%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B-%25E6%2588%25B4%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E9%2587%258D%25E7%25BD%25B0%25E9%2580%25BE%25E5%258D%2583%25E5%2585%2583-%25E5%25A5%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%2588%25A9%25E8%25A6%258F%25E5%25AE%259A%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%25B4%2599%25E6%2589%258D%25E8%2583%25BD%25E6%2588%25B4&d=Eps995EZp4R4ibMzYmnfryLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=4ca9711a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1721283%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B-%25E6%2588%25B4%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E9%2587%258D%25E7%25BD%25B0%25E9%2580%25BE%25E5%258D%2583%25E5%2585%2583-%25E5%25A5%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%2588%25A9%25E8%25A6%258F%25E5%25AE%259A%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%25B4%2599%25E6%2589%258D%25E8%2583%25BD%25E6%2588%25B4&h=fa35a1ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1721283/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E6%88%B4%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E9%87%8D%E7%BD%B0%E9%80%BE%E5%8D%83%E5%85%83-%E5%A5%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%A9%E8%A6%8F%E5%AE%9A%E6%9C%89%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E7%B4%99%E6%89%8D%E8%83%BD%E6%88%B4</a><br />\n新冠肺炎疫情肆虐歐洲，就連美國總統特朗普都歸咎大部分個案受歐洲旅客傳染，並宣布暫時禁止過去14日內到過《神根公約》26個成員國的外國人入境美國，全部是歐洲國家，但不包括英國。為防範疫情，歐洲的民眾外出都戴上口罩，不過位於歐洲的奧地利，卻因為《反蒙面法》而禁止民眾戴口罩，若違反將被罰150歐元（約港幣1297元）。駐奧地利代表處表示，即使新冠病毒肆虐，但目前在公共場合隨意戴口罩仍然違法。<br />\n<br />\n駐奧地利代表處解釋，奧地利自2017年10月1日起通過 《反蒙面法》（Anti-Gesichtsverh&uuml;llungsgesetz），在境內的地鐵、公車、戲院，甚至是馬路上，舉凡被認定為「公共場所」，沒有合理的理由就不能將臉部遮住，包含戴口罩。<br />\n<br />\n奧地利衛生部周二（10日）公布新冠肺炎採檢5362人，確診206宗、治癒返家4人；即使如此，《反蒙面法》依然禁止民眾在公共場所戴口罩。駐奧地利代表處表示，如果民眾生病，有需要戴口罩，一定要請醫生開立證明且隨身攜帶，否則可能會被警察罰款。"},{"pid":"10f6886039f53dcfaab74ec4fc07936b382d5235","tid":1939690,"uid":335434,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T09:34:56.000Z","msg":"奧地利政府對反蒙面法嘅迷戀仲勁撚過林奠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ab7bf409ae35cdf1185a709d900749967b38651","tid":1939690,"uid":212796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10f6886039f53dcfaab74ec4fc07936b382d5235","tid":1939690,"uid":335434,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T09:34:56.000Z","msg":"奧地利政府對反蒙面法嘅迷戀仲勁撚過林奠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T09:47:06.000Z","msg":"&quot;狼口&rdquo;漫畫？"},{"pid":"5035a1e93ff7bc29fda8c100c653ec77ba36d993","tid":1939690,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10f6886039f53dcfaab74ec4fc07936b382d5235","tid":1939690,"uid":335434,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T09:34:56.000Z","msg":"奧地利政府對反蒙面法嘅迷戀仲勁撚過林奠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T09:48:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />留名等睇滅國<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a723f6655d2996380707147d093915049d06ed08","tid":1939690,"uid":14941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T09:49:21.000Z","msg":"垃圾<br />\n<br />\n香港一人都非法集結啦"},{"pid":"3d272ba13976e6e9a34ed9c2f1c0201abedd7b6e","tid":1939690,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T09:54:43.000Z","msg":"又一個垃圾國家，歷史多數曾經有發達文明嘅國家啲後代都會變智障跟住自毀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cece954c9df04668d655c5d49444fdd7901c9141","tid":1939690,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d272ba13976e6e9a34ed9c2f1c0201abedd7b6e","tid":1939690,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T09:54:43.000Z","msg":"又一個垃圾國家，歷史多數曾經有發達文明嘅國家啲後代都會變智障跟住自毀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T09:56:09.000Z","msg":"其實禁蒙面法本身已經反智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1e4eae69d06ea833f6407c6947be3f1b95ba399","tid":1939690,"uid":293586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d272ba13976e6e9a34ed9c2f1c0201abedd7b6e","tid":1939690,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T09:54:43.000Z","msg":"又一個垃圾國家，歷史多數曾經有發達文明嘅國家啲後代都會變智障跟住自毀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T10:10:59.000Z","msg":"其實要有弱智人民先會有弱智政府<br />\n人民個個以為帶口罩冇用, 政府咪順理成章禁蒙面<br />\n好似香港咁, 立左蒙面法, 根本冇人理, 你立左都冇用"}]}